(38, 8, 'how-to-book', 'HOW TO BOOK', '<span class="whiteheader">HOW TO BOOK</span><br />\n<hr size="2" width="100%" />\nTickets and Festival Passes are available through The Palace George Cinemas<br />\n<br />\n<span class="uppercase">In person:</span>&nbsp; 133 - 135 Fitzroy Street, St Kilda<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 12 midday – 9pm daily<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; Cash, AMEX, Mastercard and Visa <br />\n<br />\n<span class="uppercase">By phone:</span>&nbsp; (03) 9534 6922<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 12 midday – 9pm daily<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; AMEX, Mastercard and Visa - $1 booking fee applies&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<span class="uppercase">Online:</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="http://www.palacecinemas.com.au/highlights/"> www.palacecinemas.com.au</a> &nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; AMEX, Mastercard and Visa – $1 booking fee applies<br />\n<br />\nFESTIVAL HOTLINE 03 9209 6711<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<p><span class="orangeheader">CLASSIFICATION NOTICE</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\nAs films featured in the St Kilda Film Festival are unclassified, persons under 18 years of age will not be admitted.', '2010-05-03 17:46:36', '2010-05-03 17:59:48'),
