(48, 7, 'closing-night-awards', 'Closing Night Awards', '<p><span class="whiteheader">Closing Night Awards &amp; Party</span></p>\n<hr size="2" width="100%" />\n<p><span class="uppercase">St Kilda Town Hall</span><br />\n</p>\n<span class="uppercase">Corner Carlisle St &amp; Brighton Rd, St Kilda<br />\nSunday 30 May, 8.30pm</span><br />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Join in the excitement as filmmakers battle it out to share in over $40,000 of cash and in-kind prizes across almost 20 awards – with the winner of the Best Film being awarded the richest cash prize in short film within Australia - $10,000.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Hang around after the awards and boogie the night away with a little help from TBC.</p>\n<br />\nTickets $25 Full / $20 Concession<br />\n<p>Closing Night tickets are only available from the Festival VIP Ticketing Desk at The Palace George Cinemas Foyer, during the Festival. Cash sales only.</p>\n<hr size="2" width="100%" />\n<p>&nbsp;<span class="whiteheader">AWARDS</span></p>\n<br />\n<div class="sponsor">\n<p>\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr valign="top">\n            <td width="20%">\n            <p><strong style="font-size: 10pt"><span style="color: #333333"><span style="color: #333333">BEST SHORT FILM</span></span></strong></p>\n            <span style="color: #333333"><span style="color: #333333">\n            <hr />\n            </span></span>\n            <p><span style="color: #333333">$10,000 CASH</span></p>\n            <p><span style="color: #333333">Sponsored by</span> </p>\n            <br />\n            <p><a href="http://www.portphillip.vic.gov.au/" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="/Uploads/copp.png" /></a></p>\n            </td>\n            <td width="2%"><br />\n            </td>\n            <td width="24%">\n            <p><strong style="color: #333333; font-size: 10pt">CRAFT AWARD</strong></p>\n            <hr />\n            <p><span style="color: #333333">$1,000 CASH</spa