(108, 19, 'australias-top-100-intro', 'Australia''s Top 100 Intro', '<style type="text/css">@import url(http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/css/template.css);</style>\n<style type="text/css">@import url(http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/css/template.css);</style>\n<img alt="" src="/stkildafilm/callforentries/Uploads/Top100-Intro.JPG" width="700" height="350" />\n<p>     </p>\n<br />\n<span class="page_heading"><br />\nEntries for the 2015 St Kilda Film Festival are now open<br />\n</span><br />\n<span class="page_text">Got a fab short film? We want to see your work! Enter now and you may get to see your short on the big screen in competition as one of Australia’s Top 100 short films.<br />\n<br />\nThe St Kilda Film Festival has screened films that went on to be Oscar winners and nominees, and Palme D’or winners at Cannes. A short roll call of filmmakers whose earliest works found a home at St Kilda includes Adam Elliot (Harvey Krumpet), Matthew Saville (Noise, Felony), Kriv Stenders (Red Dog), Cate Shortland (Somersault), Jane Campion (The Piano, Bright Star) and Richard Lowenstein (Dogs In Space). You could be next.<br />\n<br />\nAustralia’s Top 100 prize pool totals over $40,000 in cash and in-kind craft awards, including a $10,000 prize for Best Short Film. Other prizes include Best Director, Best Achievement in Screenplay, Best Documentary, Best Animation, Best Achievement in Cinematography, Best Achievement in Indigenous Film Making, Best Comedy and Best Achievement in Sound Post.<br />\n<br />\nMake sure you read the <span class="page_boldheading">Terms &amp; Conditions</span> and <span class="page_boldheading">Frequently Asked Questions</span> (links below), then click on Entry Form to submit your film. &nbsp;Good luck!<br />\n<br />\n<em>\nPlease note: An application fee of $33 applies for all St Kilda Film Festival entries.</em></span><span class="page_subheading"><em><br />\n</em>\n<br />\nEntries close<span class=""><span class=""> </span></span></span><span class="page_subheading"><span class="">Friday 30 January 2015</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<br />\n<span class="page_boldheading"><a class="page_boldheading" href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/page-115/frequently-asked-questions">FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class="page_boldheading"><a class="page_boldheading" href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/page-116/terms-conditions">TERMS &amp; CONDITIONS</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/page-119/screening-formats-audio-specs">SCREENING FORMATS &amp; AUDIO SPECIFICATIONS</a><br />\n<a href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/admin/page-/71"></a></span><span class="page_boldheading"><span class=""><a href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/admin/page-/71"><br />\n</a><a href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/admin/cms/page/content/71"></a></span></span><span class="page_boldheading"><span class=""><span class=""><a href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/page-71">ENTRY FORM</a><a href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/admin/cms/page/content/71"></a></span></span></span><br />\n<span class="page_boldheading"><br />\n<span class=""><a href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/page-117/how-to-post">HOW TO POST</a><br />\n<br />\n</span></span>\n<p><span class="page_boldheading"><span class=""><br />\n</span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<a href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/page-117/how-to-post"></a>', '2012-09-12 13:04:27', '2014-09-24 04:54:16'),
(109, 19, 'soundkilda-intro', 'SoundKILDA Intro', '<style type="text/css">@import url(http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/css/template.css);</style>\n<img alt="" src="/stkildafilm/callforentries/Uploads/SoundKILDA.jpg" width="700" height="350" />\n<p>     </p>\n<h1 class="page_heading"></h1>\n<p class="page_boldheading" style="text-align: justify;"><strong></strong><span class="page_heading"><br />\n<br />\nEntries are now open for SoundKILDA 2015</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class="page_text">Australia’s only dedicated music video competition, SoundKILDA, celebrates and screens music videos the way they should be – loud and large on the big screen. <br />\n<br />\nThis section of the St Kilda Film Festival is growing fast and an increased number of entries have meant high-calibre clips, bigger audiences and increased competition. The bar has been raised with all the major labels now submitting works from Australia’s premier recording artists, but we’ve seen more than one indie talent take out the top SoundKILDA prize.<br />\n<br />\nSoundKILDA Music Video Competition prizes are awarded in three categories: <span class="page_boldheading">Best Music Video</span>, <span class="page_boldheading">Best Independent Music Video</span> and <span class="page_boldheading">Best Music Video – Animation</span>.  There is also a special audience award voted for and presented on the night of the screening. Sound good? Send us your entry for your chance to win.<br />\n<br />\nPlease note: An application fee of $33 applies for all SoundKILDA entries.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class="page_subheading">Entries Close Friday 30 January 2015</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/page-115/frequently-asked-questions"><br />\n</a><a class="page_boldheading" href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/page-115/frequently-asked-questions">FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</a><a class="page_boldheading" href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/page-115/frequently-asked-questions"></a><br />\n<span class="page_boldheading"><br />\n<a href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/page-118/soundkilda---terms-conditions">TERMS &amp; CONDITIONS</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/page-119/screening-formats-audio-specs">SCREENING FORMATS &amp; AUDIO SPECIFICATIONS</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/page-70">ENTRY FORM</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class="page_boldheading"><a href="http://localhost/stkildafilm/callforentries/page-117/how-to-post">HOW TO POST</a></span><br />\n</p>\n<br />\n<p><br />\n</p>', '2012-09-12 13:39:16', '2014-09-24 05:11:10');
